This is a missed-optimization in InstCombine.

The following program reveals the missed optimization.
The source program is
```llvm
define i32 @fold_add_udiv_urem_pow2_no_mul(i32 noundef %arg) {
  %lshr = lshr i32 %arg, 4
  %and = and i32 %arg, 15
  %add = add i32 %lshr, %and
  ret i32 %add
}

```

However, current LLVM cannot optimize the source program. The expected optimized program is
```llvm
define i32 @fold_add_udiv_urem_pow2_no_mul(i32 noundef %arg) {
  %lshr = lshr i32 %arg, 4
  %and = and i32 %arg, 15
  %add = add nuw nsw i32 %lshr, %and
  ret i32 %add
}

```
